dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Columbia County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represents roads and right of way for Columbia County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Columbia_Roads_ROW_2018.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'ROADS_2018' and 'ROW_2018'.
uw_supplemental_s: For most current data, please visit http://www.co.columbia.wi.us/ColumbiaCounty/landinformation/InteractiveMapping/tabid/235/Default.aspx
